Package: fresco
Title: Flexible local regression using empirically selected control probes
Description: A R package for the preprocessing of the Illumina Human
    Methylation 450k Bead Array.  Includes functions for implementing fresco,
    a normalization method using loess regression to model and correct for
    technical artifacts.  Also includes functions to filter probes containing
    known SNPs and probes that cross-hybridize to sex chromosomes.
Version: 0.1
Author: Paul Manser <manserpt@vcu.edu>
Maintainer: Paul Manser <manserpt@vcu.edu>
License: GPL-2
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15.3),
    stats,
    methods,
    minfi